# 阿尔山·柴河旅游景区

## 景区概览

Featured Explore the Arxan-Chaihe Scenic Area in Xing'an City, Inner Mongolia! Arxan-Chaihe: A Volcanic Wonderland in the Greater Khingan Range Nestled in the heart of the Greater Khingan Range in northeastern Inner Mongolia, the Arxan-Chaihe Scenic Area spans Xing'an League and Hulunbuir. This 13,000-square-kilometer expanse is a national 5A-level "Volcanic Geological Museum," integrating Heavenly Lakes, lava formations, forests, and hot springs. It offers picturesque scenery in every season, with every step a painting. The best time to visit is from June to October: Summer boasts an average temperature of 20℃, making it a natural summer retreat; from late September to early October, the golden autumn paints the mountains with golden birches and orange-red larches, earning it the title "C


